{"tid":1394414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【真香港人】定一首屬於香港人ge歌/國歌","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:12:42.000Z","uid":278392,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3208ef432c2b519a2ba65e4fff43d447913b9ebd","tid":1394414,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"如果你支持港獨 你可以叫佢做國歌<br />\n如果唔支持港獨 可以當佢係一首代表同屬於香港人或者香港呢個地區ge歌<br />\n無論點都好 我覺得我地應該有一首代表性ge歌 抗爭ge時候可以一齊唱<br />\n<br />\n今日睇左winter on fire<br />\n同香港情況真係好似<br />\n佢地ge團結精神 我地都有<br />\n但硬係覺得差d野咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係一首屬於我地真香港人 真正愛香港ge人ge歌！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇過winter on fire ge都知道佢地抗爭ge時候一路唱烏克蘭國歌一路打狗 士氣係提升左好多 因為佢地唱緊ge係代表自己人ge歌亦係一種精神<br />\n<br />\n之前有位巴打都開過類似post 但已經沉左<br />\n宜家重新提議一次 大家集思廣益 揾一首歌黎做屬於我地ge歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗到ge淨係得海闊天空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d0592e0a861386f080596f7a5aed6c9fae004c","tid":1394414,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"213676d8cc32da60d0e522aa0e5fd3bd56d694c4","tid":1394414,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"Puuuush"},{"pid":"67d9c6e8e97f78cd312272cfcc732192fc5311b8","tid":1394414,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"15024188ee90f3575e5588d8767d191c5be29e42","tid":1394414,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66a906c2bc5751ca82fe568f3563246f4d6b85b9","tid":1394414,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0623925a8ae70bf